<p>You are right on the money about the Heal over Time spells. However, once you reach lvl 39 and get Complete Healing, it will be your most used spell from that point on. <br /> <br />What divinentia said is very true. About the only time I will draw aggro is if there are adds that don't have a player hold the aggro when a CH lands, which for me heals at least 3500 hp. What I have found is to start your CH between 40% and 45% when the mob has been slowed. If the mob hasn't been slowed, you can be starting your CH at 70% and still crossing your fingers hoping that it will heal before the MT dies.(Welcome to the Planes of Power).</p>
