<p>I'm a cleric and root is my friend. <br /> <br />I wait until the mob is 75% before I CH. I will HoT if it is needed before then.  <br /> <br />I use HoT regulargly only on support players in the group. The MT is the only one to get CH. I will only CH the main tank if I can help it since at higher levels it is the most mana efficient heal on players with more than ~3,000 HP. <br /> <br />I rarely gain agro as someone else stated above unless there is an add. Just remember root if you're a cleric, druid, shaman or enchanter. (sorry if I missed your class--no offense)</p>
